  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>\"The sun's down and the moon's pretty - it's time to ramble.\"</em></p><h5 id=\"benefit-\"><strong>Benefit:</strong></h5><p>You are a person of the night and as such have adopted to better suit the darkness of the night. You gain Darkvision. You can see in dim light within 60 feet of you as if it were bright light and in darkness as if it were in dim light. Additionally, while you are in darkness you add 1d4 to initiative checks and your movement speed is increased by 5.</p><h5 id=\"negative-\"><strong>Negative:</strong></h5><p>As a creature of the night sunlight throws you off your game. While you are in bright or dim light your movement speed is lowered by 5.</p>",
